<div id="review_2593778147" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2593778147" />
    <a title="Suzzie" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4852457-suzzie"><img alt="Suzzie" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1548981628p2/4852457.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2593778147?book_show_action=true">Nov 15, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Suzzie" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Suzzie" href="/user/show/4852457-suzzie">Suzzie</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9781538728529" href="/book/show/38245654-every-breath">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2593778147" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14653039019704652826">What a beautiful story. It just shows you how small the world can be at times. Once I started reading it, I didn’t stop. A quick one sitting read. <br/><br/>One thing I thoroughly enjoyed about this one was Nicholas Sparks’ personal words within the book. It really indicated how moved he was by the true story that inspired him in writing this book. It was lovely. There’s really no other way to put it. <br/><br/>My quick and simple overall: devastatingly beautiful ok so many fronts. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

