<span id="freeTextContainer13507679652332126234">Dreadful. Absolutely dreadful.<br/>The writing ranges from bad to atrocious.<br/>The story is cliche and unrealistic.<br/>The main characters are lifeless.<br/>The emotions are immature. <br/>The concept of love shown here is pathetically misguided.<br/>I had to read it for a book club, but urge you to not waste your time.</span>

          </span>
